清华大学是[[中华人民共和国教育部|中华人民共和国教育部]][[中央部屬高校|直属高等学校]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.moe.gov.cn/jyb_zzjg/moe_347/201508/t20150824_202647.html |title=教育部直属高等学校 |accessdate=2016-09-25 |language=zh-cn |archivedate=2016-06-20 |date=1999-04-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620005358/http://www.moe.edu.cn/jyb_zzjg/moe_347/201508/t20150824_202647.html |publisher=中华人民共和国教育部 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，名列[[211工程|211工程]]、[[985工程|985工程]]、[[雙一流|一流A類大学]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ctee.com.tw/news/viewcatenews.aspx?newsid=162072&cateid=dlcj |title=繼985和211後，陸今公布"雙一流"院校名單 |language=zh-tw |accessdate=2017-09-24 |author=李靖棠 |date=2017-09-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924072514/https://ctee.com.tw/news/viewcatenews.aspx?newsid=162072&cateid=dlcj |archivedate=2017-09-24 |publisher=工商財經數位股份有限公司 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thunews/9650/2017/20170921165632578191306/20170921165632578191306_.html |title=8所在京高校入选“一流大学” |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2017-09-24 |author=张航 |date=2017-09-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924093826/http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thunews/9650/2017/20170921165632578191306/20170921165632578191306_.html |archivedate=2017-09-24 |publisher=北京晚报 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。被公认为是中国大陆最出色的高等学府之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gvm.com.tw/Boardcontent_18006.html |title=985高校、C9聯盟名校 均以理工見長 |language=zh-tw |accessdate=2016-09-25 |author=范榮靖 |date=2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505104958/http://www.gvm.com.tw/Boardcontent_18006.html |archivedate=2013-05-05 |publisher=《遠見雜誌》 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book | author = 右灰編輯部 | title = 中國有名的大學 | location = 北京 | publisher = Hyweb Technology Co. Ltd | date = 2006-12-08 | pages = 28 | ISBN = | accessdate = 2017-03-11 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=PLcvAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT52&lpg=PT52&dq=%E5%85%AC%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%87%BA%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E5%AD%B8%E5%BA%9C%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80&source=bl&ots=MhvEQINF2k&sig=y5yZ4GWG86AQJIwYddvECw7D_YM&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwizm6ed9czSAhUE-2MKHWKPB0YQ6AEIMTAF#v=onepage&q=%E5%85%AC%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%87%BA%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E5%AD%B8%E5%BA%9C%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80&f=false | language = zh-tw | quote = | archive-date = 2017-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170312052917/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=PLcvAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT52&lpg=PT52&dq=%E5%85%AC%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%87%BA%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E5%AD%B8%E5%BA%9C%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80&source=bl&ots=MhvEQINF2k&sig=y5yZ4GWG86AQJIwYddvECw7D_YM&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwizm6ed9czSAhUE-2MKHWKPB0YQ6AEIMTAF#v=onepage&q=%E5%85%AC%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E6%9C%80%E5%87%BA%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E5%AD%B8%E5%BA%9C%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

传统上，清华大学为[[文科|文]][[理科|理]]并重<ref>{{Cite book| author =| title =信報財經月刊, 第 362-365 期| location =北京| publisher =信報有限公司| date =2007| pages =| ISBN =| accessdate =2017-09-12| url =https://books.google.at/books?id=PZGyAAAAIAAJ&q=%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E6%96%87%E7%90%86%E4%B8%A6%E9%87%8D&dq=%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E6%96%87%E7%90%86%E4%B8%A6%E9%87%8D&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiT17DPgZ_WAhWDORQKHXmCCuIQ6AEIODAD| language =zh-tw| quote =| deadurl =no| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20170912144431/https://books.google.at/books?id=PZGyAAAAIAAJ&q=%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E6%96%87%E7%90%86%E4%B8%A6%E9%87%8D&dq=%E6%B8%85%E8%8F%AF%E6%96%87%E7%90%86%E4%B8%A6%E9%87%8D&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiT17DPgZ_WAhWDORQKHXmCCuIQ6AEIODAD| archivedate =2017-09-12| df =}}</ref>。1952年[[院系调整|院系调整]]后，文理科移出，成為一所工科強勢的學校<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lib.tsinghua.edu.cn/about/history.html |title=清华大学图书馆历史沿革 |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2017-09-12 |author= |date=2017-06-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912064744/http://lib.tsinghua.edu.cn/about/history.html |archivedate=2017-09-12 |publisher=清华大学图书馆 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。改革開放以後，開始致力于建设多学科的综合性大学<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/xsg/8348/2014/20140117131127104410656/20140117131127104410656_.html |title=改革开放以来清华大学人文社会科学发展研究 |language=zh-cn |accessdate=2018-01-15 |author=李珍 王孙禺 |date=2011-06-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180114170553/http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/xsg/8348/2014/20140117131127104410656/20140117131127104410656_.html |archivedate=2018-01-14 |publisher=清华大学校史館 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，在保持工程领域的优势的形势下，其[[理科|理]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/physics-astronomy#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=the world’s top universities for physics & astronomy|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|language=en|accessdate=2016-10-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008131115/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/physics-astronomy#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-10-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/chemistry#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=the world’s top universities for chemistry|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2016-10-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008122456/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/chemistry#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-10-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/mathematics#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=the world’s top universities for mathematics|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2016-10-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008125215/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/mathematics#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-10-08}}</ref>、[[商學院|商]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/economics-econometrics#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=the world’s top universities for economics & econometrics|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2016-10-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016045858/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/economics-econometrics#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-10-16}}</ref>、[[法学|法]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/law-legal-studies#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=the world’s top universities for law|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2016-10-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827203149/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/law-legal-studies#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-08-27}}</ref>、[[新闻|新闻]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2017/communication-media-studies|title=QS World University Rankings by Subject 2017 Communication & Media Studies|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2017-07-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728091712/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2017/communication-media-studies|archivedate=2017-07-28}}</ref>、[[管理|管理]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/business-management-studies#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=top universities for business & management studies|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2016-10-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016075253/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/business-management-studies#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-10-16}}</ref>、[[生物|生物]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2017/biological-sciences|title=QS World University Rankings by Subject 2017 Biological Sciences|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2017-07-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728103008/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2017/biological-sciences|archivedate=2017-07-28}}</ref>、[[艺术|艺术]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/art-design#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|title=the world’s top universities for art & design|publisher=QS Quacquarelli Symonds|accessdate=2016-10-28|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161016070507/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2016/art-design#sorting=rank+region=+country=+faculty=+stars=false+search=|archivedate=2016-10-16}}</ref>等类专业進入世界前百。近几十年来，清华大学常被比喻为中国的[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]<ref>{{cite news |author= |title=Summers visits People's Republic of China |url= |work=HARVARD GAZETTE |format= |publisher= |date=2002-05-16 |accessdate= |ISSN= |language=en |quote= Tsinghua University, also known as the M.I.T. of China}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ntu.edu.sg/gip/GIP_2005/gip_china.htm |title=GLOBAL IMMERSION PROGRAMME(CHINA) |accessdate=2010-10-01 |author= |year=2005 |format= |work= |publisher=NanYang Technological University |pages= |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060207174909/http://www.ntu.edu.sg/gip/GIP_2005/gip_china.htm |archivedate=2006-02-07 |quote=Dubbed the MIT of China, Tsinghua University |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1999/zhufull.html |title=Transcript of Premier Zhu Rongji's speech at MIT |accessdate=2017-05-01 |author=朱镕基 |authorlink=朱镕基 |date=1999-04-15 |format= |work= |publisher=MITnews |pages= |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501062643/http://news.mit.edu/1999/zhufull |archivedate=2017-05-01 |quote=Tsinghua was called at that time the MIT of China. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但是在2017年，根據《美国新闻与世界报导》的世界大學排名，清華大學在[[工程学|工科]]領域（[[機械工程|機械]]、[[航空工程|航天]]、[[土木工程|土木]]、[[電機工程|電子電機]]）以及[[計算機科學|計算機科學]]排名世界第一<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/engineering?int=994b08 |title=Best Global Universities for Engineering |accessdate=2018-01-13 |author= |authorlink= |date=2017-10-12 |format= |work= |publisher=U.S. News & World Report |pages= |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113130701/https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/engineering |archivedate=2018-01-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/search?subject=computer-science&name= |title=Best Global Universities for Computer Science |accessdate=2018-01-13 |author= |authorlink= |date=2017-10-12 |format= |work= |publisher=U.S. News & World Report |pages= |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113131302/https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/computer-science |archivedate=2018-01-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，超越[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]]、[[史丹佛大學|史丹佛大學]]等名校<ref>{{Cite web |author=邓晖 |publisher=光明日报 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013203505/http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2015/10/328227.shtm |accessdate=2016-09-26 |date=2015-10-08 |url=http://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2015/10/328227.shtm |language=zh-cn |title=清华超越麻省理工 工程类专业排名世界第一 |archivedate=2015-10-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

对高中毕业生来说，清华是中国大陆竞争最激烈的两所学校之一，與[[北京大學|北京大學]]並稱[[清北|清北]]，每年只有中国各省市[[普通高等学校招生全国统一考试|高考]]成绩最优秀的高中毕业生才有机会被清华录取<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.zuihaodaxue.com/shengyuanzhiliangpaiming2016.html|publisher=最好大學網|accessdate=2016-11-22|title=软科中国最好大学排名-生源质量排名2016|date=2015-05-21|language=zh-cn|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122223202/http://www.zuihaodaxue.com/shengyuanzhiliangpaiming2016.html|archivedate=2016-11-22}}</ref>。清华大学的本科生毕业后相当一部分到[[美國大學列表|美国的院校]]攻读[[博士|博士]]学位，在2006年，清华是获得美国院校博士学位最多的本科生生源院校<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.taisha.org/abroad/zx/lxzx/200808/20080811162344.html |title=中国成美博士生最大生源国　九成毕业后获居留证 |accessdate=2016-09-26 |date=2008-08-11 |work= |publisher=中国侨网 |language=zh-cn |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081012231515/http://www.taisha.org/abroad/zx/lxzx/200808/20080811162344.html |archivedate=2008-10-12 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

清华大学也是国家工程科研的重要中心之一，在[[航空航天|航空航天]]、[[信息产业|信息产业]]、[[计算科学|计算科学]]、[[核物理|核物理]]、[[应用物理|应用物理]]、[[生命科技|生命科技]]等众多领域不断创造国家顶尖技术<ref name=科研成果>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/newthu/newthu_cnt/research/research-4-1.html|publisher=清華大學|accessdate=2016-09-26|title=首页 · 科学研究 · 科研成果与知识产权 · 成果奖励|language=zh-cn|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006171945/http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/newthu/newthu_cnt/research/research-4-1.html|archivedate=2016-10-06}}</ref>。

=== 学科與师生 ===
清華大學現有21個學院、59個系<ref name=統計資料/>，包含[[清华大学建筑学院|建筑]]、[[清华大学土木水利学院|土木水利]]、[[清华大学环境学院|环境]]、[[清华大学机械工程学院|机械]]、[[清华大学航天航空学院|航天航空]]、[[清华大学信息科学技术学院|信息]]、[[清华大学理学院|理学]]、[[清华大学生命科学学院|生命科学]]、[[清华大学医学院|医学]]、藥學、[[清華大學萬科公共衛生與健康學院|公衛]]、[[清华大学经济管理学院|经管]]、[[清华大学人文学院|人文]]、[[清华大学社会科学学院|社科]]、[[清华大学法学院|法学]]、[[清华大学美术学院|美术]]、[[清华大学公共管理学院|公管]]、[[清华大学新闻与传播学院|新闻]]、[[清华大学马克思主义学院|马克思主义]]、[[清华大学五道口金融学院|金融]]、[[清华大学材料学院|材料]]等。本科專業共有有82個<ref group="注">包括北京協和醫學院-清華大學醫學部的臨床醫學專業。</ref>，第二學士學位18個，[[碩士|碩士]]專業有66個，[[博士|博士]]專業則有有60個<ref group="注">包括[[北京协和医学院|北京协和医学院]]-清华大学医学部的[[临床医学|临床医学]]学位。</ref>。清華入選雙一流學科分別是[[法學|法學]]、[[政治學|政治學]]、[[馬克思主義|馬克思主義]]理論、數學、物理學、化學、[[生物學|生物學]]、[[力學|力學]]、[[機械工程|機械工程]]、儀器科學與技術、材料科學與工程、動力工程及工程熱物理、[[電氣工程|電氣工程]]、信息與[[通信工程|通信工程]]、控制科學與工程、計算機科學與技術、建築學、土木工程、水利工程、化學工程與技術、核科學與技術、環境科學與工程、[[生物醫學工程|生物醫學工程]]、城鄉規劃學、[[風景園林學|風景園林學]]、[[軟體工程|軟體工程]]、管理科學與工程、[[工商管理|工商管理]]、[[公共管理|公共管理]]、[[設計學|設計學]]、[[會計學|會計]]與[[金融|金融]]、經濟學和[[計量經濟學|計量經濟學]]、[[統計學|統計學]]與[[運籌學|運籌學]]、現代語言學等34個學科<ref>{{cite web|title=软科：10个数字解读“双一流”名单|url=http://www.zuihaodaxue.com/news/20170921-427.html|accessdate=2017-09-24|date=2017-09-21|publisher=最好大學網|language=zh-cn|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924182220/http://www.zuihaodaxue.com/news/20170921-427.html|archivedate=2017-09-24}}</ref>。
