清华大学校园基本为一个整体，形狀呈長方形，南北長2.5公里，東西寬2公里，位于[[北京市|北京市]][[海淀区|海淀区]]，[[北京四环路|北四环]]与[[北京五环路|北五环]]之间，东临[[北京地铁13号线|地铁13号线]]，西临北京大學、[[圆明园|圆明园]]。此外，建築中的光華路校區<ref>{{Cite news| author =马力| title =清华美院将在CBD建230米高楼| location =北京| publisher =新京报| url =http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2013-09/12/content_464933.htm?div=0| date =2013-09-12| accessdate =2017-07-23| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20170723041629/http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2013-09/12/content_464933.htm?div=0| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2017-07-23| deadurl =yes}}</ref>、[[清华核研院|核研院]]（[[昌平區|北京昌平]]）、[[清华大学深圳研究生院|深圳研究生院]]、附属医院以及少量疗养所、教工住宅位于校本部之外。<ref name="清华大学志：校园"/>

清华校园按照南门主路（[[学堂路|学堂路]]）分为东区、西区。西区校园为老校区，以[[美国|美]]式的校园布局和众多西洋风格的砖石结构历史建筑为特色。[[清华大礼堂|大礼堂]]为中心景观，[[清华图书馆|图书馆]]（一、二、三期工程）、[[清华科学馆|科学馆]]、[[清华学堂|清华学堂]]、[[同方部|同方部]]、[[清华西区体育馆|西体育馆]]及理学院等建筑分布其间，原王府庭园[[工字厅|工字厅]]、[[古月堂|古月堂]]、[[水木清华|水木清华]]等古建筑及[[朱自清|朱自清]]先生在《[[荷塘月色_(散文)|荷塘月色]]》中描述的“荷花池”（[[近春园|近春园]]遗址）则展示了中国传统的园林风格。东区则以1950年代兴建的[[苏联|苏]]式主楼为主体，以及建筑馆、明理楼、经管学院、逸夫科技馆等现代风格的建筑物。<ref name="清华大学志：校园">{{Cite book | author = 方惠坚，张思敬 | title = 清华大学志, 第 1 卷 | location = 北京 | publisher = 清华大学出版社 | year = 2001 | pages = 675-717 | ISBN = 7-302-04319-1 | accessdate = 2016-11-22 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=2wPeSh93IGMC&pg=PA683&lpg=PA683&dq=%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E5%BF%97%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E8%88%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86&source=bl&ots=JtOsKPFqi2&sig=xnOH8YeTEEnNy5SSW_DN84h5nnM&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiFlf2snrrQAhULi5QKHZjGBf4Q6AEIGzAA#v=onepage&q=%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E5%BF%97%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E8%88%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86&f=false | language = zh-cn | quote = | archive-date = 2017-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305003115/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=2wPeSh93IGMC&pg=PA683&lpg=PA683&dq=%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E5%BF%97%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E8%88%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86&source=bl&ots=JtOsKPFqi2&sig=xnOH8YeTEEnNy5SSW_DN84h5nnM&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiFlf2snrrQAhULi5QKHZjGBf4Q6AEIGzAA#v=onepage&q=%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E5%BF%97%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E8%88%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>

西区老校区多为[[美国|美]]式红砖建筑，东区多为白色的现代建筑<ref>{{Cite news| author =钱炜| title =清华建设中国| location =北京| publisher =清华新闻网| url =http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/news/4207/2011/20110414144622325333765/20110414144622325333765_.html| date =2011-04-14| accessdate =2018-10-22| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20181022025314/http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/news/4207/2011/20110414144622325333765/20110414144622325333765_.html| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2018-10-22| deadurl =yes}}</ref>，因此曾被一代人戏称为“[[红区|红区]]”、“[[白区|白区]]”<ref>{{cite journal |author=关悦 |year=2008 |title=施卫良：能“画出”城市未来的“魔法师” |journal=清华人 |volume= |issue=1 |language=zh-cn |publisher=清华大学校友总会 |archivedate=2016-09-17 |url=http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/news/4208/2011/20110226104120687790021/20110226104120687790021_.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917155631/http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/news/4208/2011/20110226104120687790021/20110226104120687790021_.html |deadurl=yes |access-date=2021-06-24 }}</ref>，此外东北部为紫荊学生公寓区、西北部为教工生活區與[[清华附中|清华附中]]、西南部为[[照澜院|照澜院]]社区<ref name="清华大学志：校园"/>。

清華校园内綠化程度高<ref>{{Cite web| author =陈杰人| title =杰人观察：故乡的清华柳| location =北京| publisher =天天快報| url =https://kuaibao.qq.com/s/20180305B1NT7V00?refer=spider| date =2018-03-05| accessdate =2018-10-22| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20181022040443/https://kuaibao.qq.com/s/20180305B1NT7V00?refer=spider| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2018-10-22| deadurl =yes}}</ref>，各个不同时期的建筑形成不同风格的建筑群落<ref>{{Cite web| author =董迪迪| title =看得见的历史| location =北京| publisher =清华大學校史館| url =http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/xsg/8351/2016/20161208155521789354225/20161208155521789354225_.html| date =2016-05-14| accessdate =2018-10-22| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20181022031101/http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/xsg/8351/2016/20161208155521789354225/20161208155521789354225_.html| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2018-10-22| deadurl =yes}}</ref>。截至2010年底，校园内共有[[乔木|乔木]]4.5万株、[[灌木|灌木]]20万株、[[竹子|竹子]]8.7万棵、[[宿根|宿根]]花卉4.4万株、色块27.4万株、百年以上老樹240棵。校园内的树木种类达1210种，全校绿化面积135[[公頃|公頃]]，绿化程度54.8%<ref>{{Cite news| author =| title =清华大学校园环境简介| location =北京| publisher =新浪教育| url =http://edu.sina.com.cn/gaokao/2011-06-06/0042298729.shtml| year =2011| pages =| accessdate =2016-09-11| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160915090047/http://edu.sina.com.cn/gaokao/2011-06-06/0042298729.shtml| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2016-09-15| deadurl =yes}}</ref>。

清華校园内教学與生活设施完善，全校共有6座教學樓，兩個階梯教室，面積達到5.3[[公頃|公頃]]、教室276间、座位数22806个，其中第六教学楼建筑面积3.4公頃，可容纳7500余人上课<ref name=清華校园>{{Cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916085515/http://xinwen.jgaoxiao.com/daxueshenghuo-daxuesushe-38737.html |title=清华北大校园环境大pk 全面介绍清华北大校园生活环境 |location=北京 |publisher=新浪教育 |url=http://xinwen.jgaoxiao.com/daxueshenghuo-daxuesushe-38737.html |year=2015-06-27 |pages= |accessdate=2016-08-31 |language=zh-cn |archivedate=2016-09-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>；清華擁有的学生公寓面积為50公頃，共1.457万间<ref name=清华概览/>，新建的[[紫荆学生公寓|紫荆学生公寓]]占地约28.6公顷，总建筑面积约37万平方米，位於校園北邊偏東，紫荊學生公寓區內有c樓，提供[[超市|超市]]、[[银行|银行]]、[[邮局|邮局]]等服務；校园内共有19个[[食堂|食堂]]與[[餐馆|餐厅]]，其中建筑面积为1.3万平方米的“紫荆园”是大陸高校较大的學生食堂，可容纳3000余人同时就餐<ref name=清華校园/>。

清华体育氛圍濃厚，校内体育设施先进且齐全<ref>{{Cite web| title =体育设施| location =北京| publisher =清华大学 国际学生学者中心| url =http://is.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/is_cn/9460/2015/20150602102815072469817/20150602102815072469817_.html| date =2016-09-12| accessdate =2017-10-25| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20171025102906/http://is.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/is_cn/9460/2015/20150602102815072469817/20150602102815072469817_.html| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2017-10-25| deadurl =yes}}</ref>。体育运动场地面积达22万平方公尺<ref>{{Cite web| title =清华大学的体育场馆和设施| location =北京| publisher =清华大学| url =http://chuansong.me/n/841148652636| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20171025103600/http://chuansong.me/n/841148652636| date =2014-01-20| accessdate =2017-10-25| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2017-10-25| deadurl =yes}}</ref>，有游泳馆、射击馆等专业场馆，也還有[[手球|手球]]、[[沙滩排球|沙滩排球]]、攀岩、排球、籃球、足球、棒球等专业的户外设施。擁有三個體育館，分別是西区体育馆、东区体育馆、[[清華大學综合体育馆|综合体育馆]]（又稱為「[[曹光彪|曹光彪]]体育中心」）；擁有3個操場，分別是东大操场、西大操场、紫荆操场；游泳館兩個，分別是[[清華大學西湖游泳池|西湖游泳池]]、[[陈明游泳馆|陈明游泳馆]]<ref>{{Cite web| title =运动场馆| location =北京| publisher =清华大学招生办| url =http://join-tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/bzw/7565/index.html| date =2016-09-12| accessdate =2017-10-25| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20171025105637/http://join-tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/bzw/7565/index.html| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2017-10-25| deadurl =yes}}</ref>；一個棒壘球場「北操」<ref>{{Cite web| title =热能兄弟棒球队迎战“马杯”棒球决赛| author =姜连香| location =北京| publisher =清华大学热能工程系| url =http://www.te.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/te/7582/2014/20141126095900140948934/20141126095900140948934_.html| date =2014-11-30| accessdate =2017-10-25| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20171025115640/http://www.te.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/te/7582/2014/20141126095900140948934/20141126095900140948934_.html| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2017-10-25| deadurl =yes}}</ref>、一個射擊館「维学馆」<ref>{{Cite web| title =清华大学新射击馆落成启用| author =魏磊| location =北京| publisher =清华大学新聞網| url =http://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thunews/9648/2011/20110225225333921129009/20110225225333921129009_.html| date =2009-11-09| accessdate =2017-10-25| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20171025114514/http://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thunews/9648/2011/20110225225333921129009/20110225225333921129009_.html| language =zh-cn| archivedate =2017-10-25| deadurl =yes}}</ref>。

2010年3月，美国财经杂志《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》评选出“全球最美大学校园”。入选的14个校园中，10个来自美国，3个来自欧洲，唯一上榜的亚洲院校是清华大学。福布斯认为自然环境对于校园十分重要，清华所拥有的皇家园林[[清华园|清华园]]旧址具有得天独厚的优势，紧靠[[颐和园|颐和园]]，既有传统中国式景观建筑，又有传统西式建筑和现代景观建筑。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/gj-sswh/news/2010/03-03/2147895.shtml |title=清华入选《福布斯》全球最美大学 亚洲唯一上榜 |accessdate=2017-03-30 |author= |date=2010-03-03 |format=再版 |work= |publisher=中国新闻网 |pages= |language=zh-cn |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330065452/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/gj-sswh/news/2010/03-03/2147895.shtml |archivedate=2017-03-30 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/2010/03/01/most-beautiful-campus-lifestyle-college.html |title=The World's Most Beautiful College Campuses |accessdate=2010-11-01 |author=Pascale Le Draoulec |date=2010-03-01 |format= |work= |publisher=Forbes.com |pages= |language=en |doi= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326160654/https://www.forbes.com/2010/03/01/most-beautiful-campus-lifestyle-college.html |archivedate=2017-03-26 |quote= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
