0人，排名世界第31名，中國第一<ref>{{Cite web|title=University Ultra High Net Worth Alumni Rankings 2019|url=https://www.wealthx.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Wealth-X-2019-Alumni-Report.pdf|accessdate=2019-08-04|date=2019-08-01|publisher=Wealth-X|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803174754/https://www.wealthx.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Wealth-X-2019-Alumni-Report.pdf|archivedate=2019-08-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。其他行業中，知名校友有亞洲第一位女性[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]得主[[郝景芳|郝景芳]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=科 幻 小 說 《 北 京 折 疊 》 清 華 才 女 奪 雨 果 獎|url=http://std.stheadline.com/yesterday/chi/0822eo01.html|accessdate=2017-08-15|date=2016-08-22|publisher=星島日報|language=zh-tw|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815105959/http://std.stheadline.com/yesterday/chi/0822eo01.html|archivedate=2017-08-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>、音乐人[[高晓松|高晓松]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=揭秘高晓松精彩人生：曾从清华退学 考北影落榜|url=http://www.chinanews.com/yl/2011/11-08/3445102.shtml|accessdate=2017-08-15|date=2011-11-08|publisher=中国新闻网|language=zh-cn|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815104751/http://www.chinanews.com/yl/2011/11-08/3445102.shtml|archivedate=2017-08-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=高晓松出任阿里音乐董事长|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2015-07/16/c_128025679.htm|accessdate=2017-08-15|date=2015-07-16|publisher=北京晨报|language=zh-cn|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815103848/http://news.xinhuanet.com/tech/2015-07/16/c_128025679.htm|archivedate=2017-08-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>、歌手[[李健|李健]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=大陸創作歌手李健 王菲也翻唱他作品|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201606250279-1.aspxhtml|accessdate=2017-08-15|author=繆宗翰|date=2016-06-25|publisher=中央社|language=zh-tw|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170815110533/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201606250279-1.aspx|archivedate=2017-08-15|deadurl=yes}}</ref>、[[世界圍棋大賽|世界圍棋]]冠軍[[古力|古力]]<ref>{{cite news|author1=刘洁|title=古力从清华大学毕业 围棋手都爱当学霸最认清华|url=https://sports.163.com/19/0707/21/EJGTMG3B00058782.html|work=网易体育|date=2019年7月7日|accessdate=2019-07-08|archive-date=2